text: Oscar Arnulfo Diaz Ramirez (born 31 December 1991 in San Francisco Gotera, Morazán) is a Salvadoran professional footballer who plays in the midfielder position for Central Texas Lobos FC.Central Texas Lobos He previously played for C.D. Chagüite and C.D. Fuerte San Francisco in El Salvador, where he was Captain and a fan favorite. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1991 births Category:Association football midfielders
